            "text": "<p>Whether you’ve damaged the screen, need a new battery, or are dealing with charging faults, our technicians handle every repair with precision using high-quality parts. iPads are essential tools for work, learning, and creativity, so we offer express repair options for selected models, including same-day turnaround when pre-booked.</p><p>With over a decade of experience restoring thousands of iPads, we’ve built our reputation on technical expertise, transparent pricing, and consistent service. All our iPad repairs come with a 2-year warranty for complete peace of mind.</p>"
